UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Hurry up and turn those in if you want to be declared the Master Angler!  I have been standing around here for HOURS with nothing to eat!   Hand those suckers over!' WHERE `entry`=8193;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc8`='I seek the Paragons of Power known as the Coins of the Tribes. They are the currency used by the various denizens of Zul\'Gurub, and each is imbued with subtle but powerful mojo.$B$BThere are nine distinct kinds to be found. Some are sought after by my compatriots for various armors they offer Zandalar heroes. Should you have any extra, I will trade you one of our Honor Tokens for a set of three. You may use the Tokens with Rin\'wosho the Trader; he offers our heroes special items for them.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='Excellent - this set of coins will make a fine addition to our growing collection... one that we will use in the tribe\'s defense against the rise of the Blood God. You\'ve earned this Honor Token, $N, as well as the thanks of the tribe!' WHERE `entry`=8195;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc8`='The extremely potent essence mango grows across many of the islands in the South Seas. A single mango will refresh those who eat it, both physically and mentally. If you\'ve never had one, you do yourself a disservice!$B$BWe have enough of a supply here on the isle to offer you a handful in exchange for a Zandalar Honor Token. Speak with Vinchaxa if you need to learn how to get tokens; otherwise, let\'s get to the business at hand!',`objectives_loc8`='We have enough of a supply here on the isle to offer you a handful in exchange for a Zandalar Honor Token. Speak with Vinchaxa if you need to learn how to get tokens; otherwise, let\'s get to the business at hand!',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='A fair trade, my friend - please enjoy the luscious fruits of the South Seas, with the tribe\'s blessing.' WHERE `entry`=8196;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You gained the heads!  You have halted the plundering of our gods\' power, and weakened Hakkar!$B$BYour actions are truly heroic, $N. May the heads of these troll thralls plead to you for mercy long after their blood chills.' WHERE `entry`=8201;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Thanks again, $N. Here are your tickets!' WHERE `entry`=8223;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='There be a Fishin Contest in Booty Bay this Sunday! Here are the rules for ya!' WHERE `entry`=8228;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='There is a Fishing Contest in Booty Bay this Sunday! Here are the rules for you!' WHERE `entry`=8229;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='You have learned the old ways, $N, and for that I offer you a gift from my days as a hunter.' WHERE `entry`=8232;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc8`='Welcome, welcome, welcome!  Please, $N, have a seat and discuss a simple matter with me.$B$BYou see, $N, I\'ve recently lost something dear to me, and to put it bluntly, I want it back at all costs. There\'s something in it for you, don\'t worry about that!  Oh yes, something very nice.$B$BNow, what say you $N... are you up for some adventure?' WHERE `entry`=8233;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc8`='I seek the Paragons of Power known as the Coins of the Tribes. They are the currency used by the various denizens of Zul\'Gurub, and each is imbued with subtle but powerful mojo.$B$BThere are nine distinct kinds to be found. Some are sought after by my compatriots for various armors they offer Zandalar heroes. Should you have any extra, I will trade you one of our Honor Tokens for a set of three. You may use the Tokens with Rin\'wosho the Trader; he offers our heroes special items for them.',`offerrewardtext_loc8`='Excellent - this set of coins will make a fine addition to our growing collection... one that we will use in the tribe\'s defense against the rise of the Blood God. You\'ve earned this Honor Token, $N, as well as the thanks of the tribe!' WHERE `entry`=8238;
